-TASER! TASER! TASER!

00:19.033 --> 00:21.467
-OW! OW!
-* BAD BOYS, BAD BOYS

00:21.567 --> 00:23.167
-* WHATCHA GONNA DO
-THEY'RE RUNNING.

00:23.267 --> 00:25.433
-* WHATCHA GONNA DO
